Some tips to play :
- You go faster on infected cells;
- More you control cells, less leukocytes appear;
- Eat erythocytes (red ones) heals you;
- It can not be more than 25 leukocytes in the same room;
- It can not be more than 1 bullet on screen at the same time, so : closer you are to your target, faster you can shoot!
- Start to aim easy quests that rewards bonus, they will not disappear if you die!

Have fun! ;-)
